---
title: Chicken, Roasted Asparagus and Tomato Stovetop Risotto with Italian Style Cheese and Balsamic Drizzle
description: Making a risotto on the hob or stove is simpler than you think, with only three stirs needed to absorb the stock and flavours. This Chicken, Roasted Asparagus and Tomato Stovetop Risotto is topped with seasonal favourite asparagus.
